        Creates a new ButtonSubmit with given dimensions. The text from the given TextField is used to create a new player. The label over the TextField will change to contain the submitted text.
        Parameters:
        textField - The TextField containing the submitted text
        dimensions - The size of the button
        players - The list of players
        label - The label over the TextField
